<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{حَتَّى يَأْذَنَ لِي أَبِي}</span>:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قدّمَ المجرورَ لأنَّهُ المقْصودُ لا مطلق الإذْنِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{أَوْ يَحْكُمَ اللَّهُ لِي}</span>:<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">أي:</span> بغيرِ إِذْنِ الأب؛ لأنهُ بحكمٍ من اللَّهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٨١ - <span class="c3">{ارْجِعُوا}</span>:<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>للوجوب.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{فَقُولُوا}</span>:<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>للإرْشادِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c3">{وَمَا كُنَّا}</span>:<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>الواوُ إِمَّا عاطفةٌ، أوْ واوُ الحَال.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c3">{وَمَا كُنَّا لِلْغَيْبِ حَافِظِينَ}</span>:<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>اعْتذارٌ،<span class="c5"> أي:</span> لوْ علِمْنا أَن الأمر يؤُولُ لِمَا وقعَ، لَما شهِدْنا عليه.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>